cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV. 

This paper is about improving the performance of neural machine translation models, which is a natural language processing task. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also proposes a strategy using reinforcement learning, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The proposed framework involves refining the source representations, which is a machine learning task and could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper uses experimental results to evaluate the proposed approach, which could fall under cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as it involves analyzing and interpreting data.
